{"tid":168314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"救命呀 真係好鐘意佢呀","createTime":"2017-03-23T12:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T13:23:56.000Z","uid":47146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec10f265bfd3e44ebdf5c522edf758a8bc9a9dd0","tid":168314,"uid":47146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"可唔可以聽下毒撚心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同佢傾偈好開心 好鐘意聽到佢把聲<br />\n有時佢會主動撩我講野 講東講西乜都講一餐<br />\n返學日日都會見到佢 佢一出現眼前就好開心<br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解面對面時大家好好傾 佢會主動同我講野<br />\n當見唔到面時WhatsApp佢 佢好似hea答我 有時來回傾左幾句就已讀不回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想話比佢知 同佢一齊ge時間好舒服<br />\n好想好想同佢一齊 可以為佢做好多好多野<br />\n但好驚其實比人fdzone左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知自己係佢心中咩地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都幾肯定佢同其他同學冇咁close咁多偈傾<br />\n<br />\n究竟我係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35af3fe53793f542a85d348da1e752374c70274","tid":168314,"uid":69418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"兵？"},{"pid":"d4044dd8aca2c9ed14ced167844158b354ff07f5","tid":168314,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"不如坦白當面同佢講<br />\n你會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa566e972eda73dee4a566e5c499d3fba4521e0","tid":168314,"uid":47146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兵？</blockquote><br />\n最唔想聽到就係呢個答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1960f104159a709f31dcf17e52d8c5add07071ff","tid":168314,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚"},{"pid":"222da455512177ae0f1fe7b6ca792fc1b9b46011","tid":168314,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited